1
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:26,199
Lady An,

2
00:00:32,020 --> 00:00:33,119
where did you get the lotus

3
00:00:33,740 --> 00:00:35,420
in this freezing winter?

4
00:00:36,619 --> 00:00:37,700
I specially brought them from the south.

5
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:39,780
Eight horses died on the way.

6
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,479
But if it can make you smile,

7
00:00:41,979 --> 00:00:42,740
it's all worth it.

8
00:00:45,460 --> 00:00:46,560
I appreciate

9
00:00:46,799 --> 00:00:47,679
your kindness.

10
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,299
But

11
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:51,880
I feel guilty

12
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:53,619
I feel unworthy of it.

13
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,340
So that's how it is.

14
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:03,320
Your compassion

15
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,340
is not for me after all.

16
00:01:25,260 --> 00:01:26,659
Lotus stands in the mud,

17
00:01:27,019 --> 00:01:28,120
yet remains pure.

18
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,980
Your power should be the same.

19
00:01:33,180 --> 00:01:35,239
The menial tasks in the office

20
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:36,640
are like dust in the wind,

21
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:39,459
meaningless to you.

22
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,780
I implore you,

23
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:44,680
to grant them a chance at survival.

24
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,560
It would also

25
00:01:47,579 --> 00:01:49,459
bring you inner peace.

26
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:55,879
Lady An, do you know

27
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,159
that I am also just a handful of mud?

28
00:02:01,180 --> 00:02:02,980
The world sees only the Xie family's glory

29
00:02:04,019 --> 00:02:05,079
and the prestige of the Hundred Treasures Decree,

30
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:07,340
but they do not realize

31
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:10,740
that between my father and the court,

32
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,120
I never even had

33
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,840
[a choice to be a pawn]

34
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:17,080
[between them.]

35
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,659
[You paint lotus,]

36
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:31,580
[but I'm]

37
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,120
[just the filthy nutrient]

38
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:37,120
[under it.]

39
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:52,439
[Lotus seed]

40
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,580
[is refreshing,]

41
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,740
[but its heart]

42
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:03,259
[is inflammable.]

43
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:11,180
It's getting late.

44
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:12,439
Lady An,

45
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,639
I'll escort you back to your room.

46
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,159
My Lord,

47
00:03:20,979 --> 00:03:21,539
are you alright?

48
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:36,520
If you are truly compassionate,

49
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:40,120
could you forgive my sins?

50
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,699
Hand over your sins

51
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,620
to me,

52
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:53,520
and I'll grant you peace.

53
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,740
[You must rescue Mu Qing]

54
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:51,560
[before the drug wears off.]

55
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,420
My lord,

56
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,100
you're awake.

57
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:19,660
My lord,

58
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:20,939
last night...

59
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:25,379
From now on,

60
00:06:25,899 --> 00:06:26,879
I hope you

61
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,879
take care of yourself.

62
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:31,980
With you here,

63
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:34,040
how could I not?

64
00:06:37,899 --> 00:06:38,980
I was out of line last night.

65
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,860
It was all

66
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,360
my fault.

67
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,019
I promise you,

68
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:46,720
I'll never kill anyone again.

69
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,600
I'll let go of

70
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:49,959
those innocent people.

71
00:06:51,019 --> 00:06:51,939
After this,

72
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:01,439
I'll marry you

73
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,339
in a proper way.

74
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,500
I'll never

75
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:10,839
let you down.

76
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,240
How dare you!

77
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,779
How dare you barge into my bedroom!

78
00:07:31,139 --> 00:07:32,139
Su Luoyao,

79
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:35,160
you're being cruel to me.

80
00:07:37,699 --> 00:07:38,980
By order of the Prince of Lin'an,

81
00:07:39,579 --> 00:07:41,160
I'm here to interrogate Xie Huaiyun.

82
00:07:43,339 --> 00:07:44,139
You disobedient son!

83
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:46,300
How dare you use the royal seal

84
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,319
to release a dangerous criminal!

85
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,379
Do you still have any respect for the law?

86
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,699
Do you still have any respect for the Xie family?

87
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,139
Father, since you've already made up your mind,

88
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,180
why bother asking?

89
00:08:00,019 --> 00:08:01,339
I did release the servant.

90
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,480
I'll take full

91
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,800
responsibility.

92
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,420
What can you possibly do to make amends?

93
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,899
The arson case remains unsolved.

94
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:10,920
How dare you release the prisoner?

95
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:11,819
How dare?

96
00:08:11,819 --> 00:08:13,079
Then how dare we take a life?

97
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,500
Father,

98
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:19,560
you've been in power for too long.

99
00:08:20,860 --> 00:08:21,600
Do you still remember

100
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,800
the feeling of blood on your hands?

101
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:25,959
Does it burn your hands?

102
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,680
Does it chill your heart?

103
00:08:28,339 --> 00:08:29,120
Bastard!

104
00:08:33,059 --> 00:08:33,639
This wound

105
00:08:34,779 --> 00:08:35,700
has been gnawing at my bones

106
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:37,639
since the night of the massacre eight years ago.

107
00:08:38,940 --> 00:08:40,539
Every day since then.

108
00:08:42,279 --> 00:08:43,440
Every scar is asking

109
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,399
what we deserve.

110
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:49,399
Power.

111
00:08:50,299 --> 00:08:51,019
Fame and fortune.

112
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:54,139
This bloodstained illusionary dream.

113
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,700
It's time for us to wake up.

114
00:09:10,820 --> 00:09:11,659
Lingfeng.

115
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:13,639
Lingfeng.

116
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:18,700
Father.

117
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,259
From now on,

118
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,759
Xie Huaiyun is stripped of his position,

119
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,879
and confine him to the residence.

120
00:09:26,019 --> 00:09:26,940
He is not allowed to go out.

121
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:28,960
Xie Lingfeng will

122
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:30,879
take over the position temporarily.

123
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,019
Yes, father.

124
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,080
Take him away.
Yes.

125
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:37,779
Please.
